{"tid":555945,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲可以講下饒宗頤到底有咩學術成就？","createTime":"2018-02-10T04:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T05:51:57.000Z","uid":164920,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef0ca5a11d38f949f72ed86608f84888f31025d","tid":555945,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"個個都話饒宗頤好勁，但佢既學術成果究竟大概講乜野？佢啲作品好似大部分都係又專又僻既考據，除此之外佢有無咩成果改寫左學術界既共識咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0eeb721a491732b5f723563c21e9340506afe3d","tid":555945,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"拍咗導火新聞線、一路向西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb4b9390d0daae6ff47f7d49bf946d8e1e0b496","tid":555945,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0eeb721a491732b5f723563c21e9340506afe3d","tid":555945,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"拍咗導火新聞線、一路向西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:33:36.000Z","msg":"𨳒你老母"},{"pid":"65b94f0def8bb61c34c881f1cd401ed78b7768ea","tid":555945,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ajti.gov.mo/CN/detail/1/AcademicAchievements\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ajti.gov.mo%2FCN%2Fdetail%2F1%2FAcademicAchievements&d=h3oADuDJK3jSendkQNSAcePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=033a205b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ajti.gov.mo/CN/detail/1/AcademicAchievements</a>"},{"pid":"ee24642a71c772e92feb61fcaec99046d81d32b5","tid":555945,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b94f0def8bb61c34c881f1cd401ed78b7768ea","tid":555945,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ajti.gov.mo/CN/detail/1/AcademicAchievements\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ajti.gov.mo%2FCN%2Fdetail%2F1%2FAcademicAchievements&d=h3oADuDJK3jSendkQNSAcePnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=033a205b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ajti.gov.mo/CN/detail/1/AcademicAchievements</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"饒宗頤先生家學淵源，天資聰穎，7歲著《後封神演義》；10歲能讀《史記》；16歲時咏《優曇花詩》，一時詩壇諸老宿競與唱和，享神童之譽，詩作發表於中山大學中文系《文學雜誌》1934年第11期。1932年，其父饒鍔先生病逝，饒宗頤先生繼承父志續編《潮州藝文志》，刊於《嶺南學報》1935年第4卷及1937年第6卷，成為研究潮州歷代文獻的里程碑著作，共計65萬字。"},{"pid":"7d5aa98758092ebc31b29a391ebeb4cd235e73f3","tid":555945,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"1946至1949年擔任《潮州志》總編纂兼廣東省文獻委員會委員，以新材料、新體例和新方法編撰該志。全書設30門類專門分志，其中1949年出版15門類共20分册，2005年、2011年補刊餘下之大部，題材及體例皆精研創新，為中國地方志的一個開創性典範，至今仍為編寫地方志的圭臬。"},{"pid":"ce960e6d1328988d759956b3bce94dc6d2bbb14a","tid":555945,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"1976年，先生第三次到法國巴黎，在遠東學院工作，並追隨蒲德侯(Jean Bottero)學習巴比倫文，開始研究上古楔形文字和西亞上古文獻，後以多年時間將一部以楔形文字記述阿克得人開天闢地的神話集(乃西亞神典，世界最早的史詩之一)翻譯成中文，在1991年出版《近東開闢史詩》，為巴比倫史詩之第一部中譯本。"},{"pid":"45facdaa9d22f52058b35765311fac27e0d29186","tid":555945,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce960e6d1328988d759956b3bce94dc6d2bbb14a","tid":555945,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"1976年，先生第三次到法國巴黎，在遠東學院工作，並追隨蒲德侯(Jean Bottero)學習巴比倫文，開始研究上古楔形文字和西亞上古文獻，後以多年時間將一部以楔形文字記述阿克得人開天闢地的神話集(乃西亞神典，世界最早的史詩之一)翻譯成中文，在1991年出版《近東開闢史詩》，為巴比倫史詩之第一部中譯本。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}